{
  "texts": [
    "There was a need for 3 clusters, each comprising 11 phases.",
    "This configuration was influenced by the frequency distribution having three distinct concentration regions.",
    "The histogram in Figure 6 displays multimodal data with a CoV of 0.51.",
    "Data sets of this nature pose significant challenges when attempting fitting using traditional distributions.",
    "However, with the algorithm discussed in this text, 3 clusters were required, each consisting of 49 phases."
  ]
}